      "side": 1,
      "message": "[warning] Line 123: Clearing body overwrites unconditionally for every conversation that contained the removed handler can erase overwrites that are still owned by other enabled chat handlers. At this point `toggledSet.erase(...)` may leave `toggledSet` non-empty, so another plugin remains toggled for the same conversation. Please only clear when the removed handler was the last toggled handler for that conversation, or make the clear operation handler-scoped if overwrites are per handler.\n\n```suggestion\n                    if (toggledSet.empty()) {\n                        toClearOverwrites.push_back(key);\n                    }\n```",
      "revId": "d621794713b4a6fb8fca4fc9102df48d40515057",
